name: Saber
desc: —Knight of the Sword and Heroic Spirit of the Sword. A jack-of-all-trades warrior. Agile and powerful in close quarters; extremely adept at swordsmanship.—

name: Pretender
desc: —Those who have given false representation, deceiving and misleading others to do great deeds. Not a fake or counterfeit, but someone who deceives even the soul until more power and greater achievements than the real thing remain.—

name: Beast
desc: —The Beasts of Calamity symbolizing the seven Evils of Man. The archetype of the Heroic Spirit Summoning System as well as the enemies of the Grand Servants.—
